==反响==
《边缘战士》上映后获得了较为负面的评价<ref>{{cite news|title= Raw Deal|publisher= Variety|date=1985-12-31|url= http://variety.com/1985/film/reviews/raw-deal-1200426826/ |accessdate=2013-05-28}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title= Raw Deal|publisher= Chicago Sun Times|date=|url= http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/raw-deal-1986 | accessdate=2013-05-28}}</ref>，根据[[烂蕃茄|烂蕃茄]]上收集的12篇专业评论文章，仅有3篇给出了“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度”为25%，平均得分3.8（满分10分）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1017226-raw_deal/ |title=Raw Deal|work=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2013-05-28}}</ref>。不过《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》的席拉·本森虽然批评电影中的暴力元素，但还是对施瓦辛格的演出表示赞赏<ref>{{cite news|title=Movie Review : A 'Raw Deal' For Audience, Cast And Crew|publisher=The Los Angeles Times|date=1986-06-06|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1986-06-06/entertainment/ca-8980_1_raw-deal|accessdate=2013-05-28|first=Sheila|last=Benson|archive-date=2012-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121104022848/http://articles.latimes.com/1986-06-06/entertainment/ca-8980_1_raw-deal|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===票房===
《边缘战士》于1986年6月6日起上映，首周1731家电影院共获得543万8978美元的票房收入，名列排行榜亚军，最终在美国本土入账1620万9459美元<ref>{{cite web|title= Raw Deal (1986) |publisher= Box Office Mojo |url= http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=rawdeal.htm | accessdate=2013-05-28}}</ref>，在德国上映也收入了218万3216美元<ref>{{cite web|title=IMDB Box Office Stats|url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0091828/business}}</ref>。虽然电影票房收入已经远超过制作成本，但制片商对此仍然表示失望<ref>{{cite news|title=Schwarzenegger Vs. Stallone: 'Deal' Strikes First|publisher=The Los Angeles Times|date=1986-10-03|url=http://articles.latimes.com/1986-10-03/entertainment/ca-3887_1_raw-deal|accessdate=2013-05-28|first=Dennis|last=Hunt|archive-date=2012-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121224041505/http://articles.latimes.com/1986-10-03/entertainment/ca-3887_1_raw-deal|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

